<div class="a2">To: <b>eastforker</b></div>
<div class="b2">
    <p>In a sense, we have that already.</p>
<p>Something like 97% of the &#8220;wealth&#8221; in this country isn&#8217;t in cash - it&#8217;s in Savings and checking accounts, Stocks, Certificates of deposit, 401(k)s..</p>
<p>If the grid goes down, for many if not most people, what you got is whatever you got stuffed under your mattress, or coins lost in your couch. That&#8217;s it!</p>

